import React from 'react'; function About() { return (

HERE I AM

I am Junior Full Stack web developer and I based in London, UK.
I am looking for full-stack developer roles and available for interviews any time.
My colleagues and my friend would describe me as someone who is self-motivated,
hardworking, proactive, caring and dedicated person.
I have a wide range of transferable skills in software development and IT infrastructure.
I am a team player capable of adapting well to new circumstances and conditions, and problem solver.
I can adapt to new environments quickly and love learning. Currently seeking a role as a Full Stack web developer.

); } export default About;
